# Music OS (private routes)

Private admin at `/studio`, `/journey`, `/releases`. Full spec: @docs/PROJECT_BRIEF.md · Data: @docs/DATA_MODEL.md

**Auth:** `/login` + middleware (httpOnly cookie, `MUSIC_OS_PASSWORD`, ~1 year). WeekOS pattern.
No sign-up, email, or OAuth.

**`/studio`:** Intention block → Reflection block → AI Coach chat (always visible below).

**`/journey`:** weekly focus + weekly reflection (tiny win required) + plain session list (no graphs).

**`/releases`:** song cards with stages (discovering → shared), comfort level, notes, optional target.
Pre-load "Knockin' on Heaven's Door" — Bob Dylan.

Stages are states, not deadlines. No quantitative analytics. Coach: @docs/AI_COACH.md
